# Pricing & Plans

## Free Plan
- Limited access to the knowledge base
- Up to 20 queries per month
- Community support only

## Professional Plan
- Unlimited document queries
- Priority support
- Monthly billing

## Enterprise Plan
- Custom pricing
- Dedicated account manager
- On-premise deployment options
- SLA-backed support

Enterprise pricing is determined based on usage volume,
security requirements, and integration complexity.

Product Overview

The Internal Knowledge Assistant allows users to ask natural language questions
about company documentation and receive context-aware answers.

The system is designed to prevent hallucinations by answering only from
verified internal sources.

If relevant information cannot be found with sufficient confidence,
the assistant defers to human customer support.

Refund Policy

We offer a 14-day refund window for all standard subscription plans.
Customers may request a refund within 14 days of the initial purchase date,
provided that the service has not been abused or used in violation of our terms.

Refunds are not available for:
- Enterprise contracts
- Custom integrations
- Services that have already been fully delivered

Refund requests must be submitted through customer support and may take
510 business days to process once approved.

If a subscription is canceled after the refund window, access will remain
active until the end of the current billing cycle.

Security & Privacy

All customer data is encrypted in transit using TLS 1.2 or higher.
Sensitive information is never logged or stored in plain text.

Uploaded documents are used exclusively for retrieval purposes and are not
used to train machine learning models.

Access to internal systems is restricted based on role-based access control (RBAC).
Regular security audits are conducted to ensure compliance with internal policies.

For security-related inquiries, customers should contact support directly.
